platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Vector art is remarkably useful—you can create completely scalable works simply by manipulating a variety of shapes. Assembly shines with accessible and intuitive features that let designers of all skill levels quickly add gorgeous objects to their photos or make artwork from the ground up. Thanks to a refined interface, you can alter your drawings easily on both iPad and iPhone. Plus, with a suite of smart sharing tools, it’s easy to collaborate with other designers.
